{"tid":49271,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大局已定 - 12月22號谷中位置4串5 另加兩大馬房來料","createTime":"2016-12-21T14:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T03:26:11.000Z","uid":52970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ab2af43079300d6984fa71c3e286dde369e49c","tid":49271,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"大局已定系列，每個賽事，提供4隻位置馬以供參考，4串5 刀仔鋸大樹<br />\n如圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/21/224341_3ca55df04e20a870b6e86a444af8daac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F21%2F224341_3ca55df04e20a870b6e86a444af8daac.jpg&h=8573e84f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12月22號谷草提供4隻以作參考:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m0794T9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm0794T9.jpg&h=8e5276f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1場12號金武士<br />\n5場6號家多福<br />\n7場9號海都巨星<br />\n8場2鄉村輝煌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬房分析: 本人重點研究幾個馬房操練及部署<br />\n<br />\n蔡摩馬房來料，<br />\n蔡三隻都應該會去馬，<br />\n哈哈爸爸，增程600，前置型馬，短直路岩，而且好檔相信唔係亂黎。戰利品1600上2000照贏，切忌備忘。<br />\n升龍，上仗跑法用上生手鄭朗升，後追第3，4班應屬超班，<br />\n冷門 鄉村輝煌，1200贏馬路程，蔡生皇牌，兩場熱身，試3課閘，不能遺忘<br />\n<br />\nJohn size 一貫熱食，冷馬不多但都會有，所以大多ching都會留意到<br />\n<br />\n大摩: 有興趣再講。"},{"pid":"a8e9e4c90702ae58a1e1e0586dbcf00f917d839f","tid":49271,"uid":26531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:53:30.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"b7463528ddbf44c2de45c3efe5334dc36947bc71","tid":49271,"uid":23354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4edfa0762b7e81026951a6164a829cbc2c2367fd","tid":49271,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3408dca8dffef0b7bf9fd790ca78cb48b8c53eab","tid":49271,"uid":23354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"邊撚度有升龍呢隻馬"},{"pid":"9c7d22b24b231335175dbed18c70f4d3690934b0","tid":49271,"uid":52197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"28f818fbc2b0b8be82aaf9f0e261a525e664822e","tid":49271,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊撚度有升龍呢隻馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文盲講馬，同動物溝通唔識字"},{"pid":"6c554251aaf03ece25d35037ba46076794a0ff12","tid":49271,"uid":53404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"be282049678720425c7c653f7b85f37dfad669fc","tid":49271,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8e85aeac529c7aefa5aaf9886aa3049e99d086cd","tid":49271,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"大家有咩心水不彷討論下"},{"pid":"6d4d1b4f2cccb36c79a4a013aff961d7c4351fd2","tid":49271,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"嘉鈴巴打留名"},{"pid":"c8318473aa206f8b7fe915d689f7eb55e241c6b4","tid":49271,"uid":9913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚有信心又大局已定 都係買得20蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n50蚊3串7都唔笑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8267577a4d3b5985bc43017de7119a094f9f82","tid":49271,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c76f01e0539f6fb0aacefe3e2f0bbf6757adea4","tid":49271,"uid":11420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:54:09.000Z","msg":"點解睇好r1 12"},{"pid":"c4be243a986c73600b1ed0db7ba874d4b70291b3","tid":49271,"uid":68616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"貼張真飛睇睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8933802ca94d6be5f97cab512d09e17ee231910c","tid":49271,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚有信心又大局已定 都係買得20蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n50蚊3串7都唔笑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單場分開買已補，過關小注，星期六豐收日，財神傾心星未計"},{"pid":"fbc0a10a99c50f13c46a5da7efe05d53a011033d","tid":49271,"uid":23354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"貼飛"},{"pid":"5df46b095159b04bf24942e53737e115028f63f6","tid":49271,"uid":65160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊撚度有升龍呢隻馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文盲講馬，同動物溝通唔識字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣同韋巴講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c566537ce24e71982295bd9d7deca979cb181330","tid":49271,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚有信心又大局已定 都係買得20蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n50蚊3串7都唔笑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n再加上，留意返當日呢注係第一注飛 你甘買中當然好，但死左，後面就冇本買單場，所以先甘細注。<br />\n頭場神駒做膽食餐已收錢，雷神頂住條q先變得冇甘好分。 每日限本係我既玩法，贏左先加注。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61mSPq9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61mSPq9.jpg&h=4faa403b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每注買幾多，每個人都唔同既，不喜勿插"},{"pid":"9d97eb84c3a364910c1ba975ab10b55f98a0f9b1","tid":49271,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊撚度有升龍呢隻馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文盲講馬，同動物溝通唔識字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣同韋巴講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n改左名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e475ad4e291a5309be92e883f1fbbb9c836e2847","tid":49271,"uid":65160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文盲講馬，同動物溝通唔識字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣同韋巴講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n改左名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該就係啦<br />\n禁起底個掣見到啲舊post"},{"pid":"ceed0ae9c22970808c327dd26354953c3b458ceb","tid":49271,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解睇好r1 12</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多報紙佬都話減分，41分落5班，減分使乜用蘇兆輝，唔用華將？自己諗下。估計柏寶潘狗呢d造唔到磅，先要用蘇仔，而留意下徒弟Vincent ho騎咩？愛寶1200上一哩，放唔到係前面先奇。個人認為做電兔。<br />\n金武士今季一出即勝, 前仗,谷草1200米, 排9檔出閘,一早捉在後面貼欄, 直路揾位沖一段,早早收工,似試馬性質, 走勢不弱,只輸3個多馬位, 上仗轉跑泥地, 血統有支持, 亦是一早捉在後面, 直路揾位內欄追返第五, 證明狀態一定無問題. 兩仗出閘迅速,都捉在後面, 反應有一定前速,餘勢亦好, 增程1650米一定岩跑, 5檔亦可守在中間或者甚至前面有遮檔競跑, 復課後晨操觀感亦好. 換上蘇兆輝,後上馬騎功比炒飯更扎實。5歲馬持續進步，41分使乜等落班，輕磅好檔一樣岩跑，傑仔寶藏切勿遺忘。<br />\n都有小小主觀願望跑得好，初出有買收錢感情分。<br />\n<br />\n個人見解，不喜勿插。"},{"pid":"3a0884baab8b4f9b234b453d823662859cd2b12c","tid":49271,"uid":52970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣同韋巴講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n改左名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該就係啦<br />\n禁起底個掣見到啲舊post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇睇 sor9 希望韋巴大量"},{"pid":"90cb3433a76947515e979f832a56713259f4d4a3","tid":49271,"uid":23354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b86bf0113595fba558e9e9f6378821b709c3cbb","tid":49271,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:16:10.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}